<D>__{bullshit.}
<C>__{carol}
<D>__{i mean it.}
<C>__{doc}
<D>__{i know you do. but it is different.}
<P>__{(before she can interrupt suddenly up a notch)}
<D>__{it's different.}
<P>__{(quieting down)}
<D>__{we'll be all right tomorrow.}
<C>__{carol}
<D>__{we are always going to be all right tomorrow. i'd like to be all right a few todays.}
<C>__{doc}
<D>__{we're going to have a lot of those,}
<P>__{(easy, embracing her tightly)}
<D>__{we're just going to get the money and then go all the way.}
